1. Initialization
    a. Create S3 Bucket
    b. Create DB on RDS
    c. Configure parameters
    d. Deploy using aws eb
2. System Init
    a. Create/Update schema
    b. Create basic roles
    c. Create admin users
    d. Create sample teacher/student/parent users
    e. Fill access control table
3. Setup
    a. System settings page
4. Routes
    a. User Management
        1) Staff Management
            a) Add/remove staff
            b) Update staff role
            c) Update staff profile
            d) Add/remove teacher subjects
            e) Find staff
        2) Applicant registration
            - Only against an exam
        3) Existing student
            a) Add/remove/update
            b) Find by name, username, class, section, stream, fathername, city
    b. Class Management
        1) Add/remove/update class name
            a) Add/Remove/Update stream, auto-create stream if none added
            b) Add/Remove/Update sections, auto-create one section if none added
            c) Create classes automatically from 1st to nth
        2) List all classes, streams, sections
        3) Add/remove/update subjects
        4) Add/remove subjects to class/stream
    